# Create a case-insensitive directory on Linux

 [1] : Select folder
 [2] : Create Mount
 [3] : Remove a mount
 [4] : Make existing mount permanent

You can also make select and make a folder, then move
over an existing application with a GitHub repo.
Do not delete MountScript, because the images are saved here.

Type "q" to quit
